channel.title: Prayer orb
channel.description: I was removing a lot of clusters server sided that i didnt want, literally kinda even deleted full files and then fixed the errors, everything was working fine, but when i tried to login, the client had an error loading the prayer orb and froze, i used the client on another server and it worked, so i commented out the prayer orb loading and now it works, but i thought the orbs where added client sided and im pretty sure i didnt remove the prayer points, is there something else i could've screwed server-sided?
